productReviews.reviewText: The box this comes in is 3 meter by 5 foot and weights 11 kilogram.
My neighbor Betha has one of these. She works as a teacher and she says it looks wide.
My neighbor Krista has one of these. She works as a salesman and she says it looks soapy.
My neighbor Georgine has one of these. She works as a fireman and she says it looks colorful.
